          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-1" n="1">I'd have you to know as sure as you're Dean</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-2" n="2">On Thursday my Cask of Obrien I'll drein</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-3" n="3">If my Wife be not willing I say she's a Quean</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-4" n="4">And my right to the Cellar I gad I'll maintain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-5" n="5">As bravely as any that fought at Dunblain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-6" n="6">Go tell her it over and over again.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-7" n="7">I hope as I ride to the Town it wont rain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-8" n="8">For shou'd it I fear it will cool my hot Brain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-9" n="9">Entirely extinguish my Poetick vein,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-10" n="10">And then I shou'd be as stupid as Kain,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-11" n="11">Who preach'd on three Heads tho' he mention'd but twain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-12" n="12">Now Wardels in hast and begins to complain</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-13" n="13">Your most humble Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> dear Sir I remain</l>
            <l rend="indent(6)" xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-14" n="14">|||||T── S────n</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-15" n="15">Get Helsham Walmsley Delany</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-16" n="16">And Some Grattens if there be any</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X16-CWJS-line-17" n="17">Take care you do not bid too many.</l>
          </lg>
